node.text: So honored to team up with @bose to celebrate healthcare heroes in Cincinnati. Visit soundsanctuary.bose.com to nominate your own hero. #TeamBose #SBLV

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Joe Burrow on January 19, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: Unfortunately I wasn’t able to wear these cleats on the field, but I’m proud to support the Athens County Food Pantry and all of the incredible work they do. I appreciate all of the students in the @athenscitysd who submitted design ideas, and a special thank you to Nikki Bean for her artwork that inspired the final concept. These autographed cleats will be available for auction with proceeds benefitting the food pantry. Link in bio!
